data.description: Nearly new Baessler built home in convenient Promontory! Easy commute to all northern Colorado cities and move-in ready. Stainless steel kitchen appliances including gas stove and refrigerator, high efficiency furnace and central air, walk-in closet, mudroom off the garage, upstairs laundry, Ring doorbell, security system. Yard is fully fenced with sprinkler system. Enjoy the community park and living with beautiful views of the front range! Home warranty included.
data.whatILove: No backyard neighbor, close to neighborhood park, south-facing driveway, upstairs laundry
